Package: rtemis
Version: 1.0.0
Title: Machine Learning and Visualization
Date: 2026-02-02
Authors@R: person(given = "E.D.", family = "Gennatas", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), 
    email = "gennatas@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9280-3609"))
Description: A machine learning and visualization package with an 'S7' backend 
    featuring type checking and validation, paired with a functional API. 
    'train()', 'cluster()', and 'decomp()' provide one-call access to supervised 
    and unsupervised learning. 'setup_' functions provide validated configuration 
    for each step. A single call to 'train()' handles preprocessing, training, 
    hyperparameter tuning, and testing with nested resampling. Supports 
    'data.frame', 'data.table', and 'tibble' inputs, parallel execution, and 
    interactive visualizations. The package first appeared in 
    <https://repository.upenn.edu/entities/publication/d81892ea-3087-4b71-a6f5-739c58626d64>.
